		<div class="comment-body"><p>Nice article! I can&#8217;t work out why the cross product of the vectors only gives an approximate arc length, but it is Monday after all.</p>
<p>Also, shouldn&#8217;t L have the same length as t? I know this isn&#8217;t too helpful as finding the length of t is a slow operation, but it seems worth mentioning.</p>
</div>

